data.description: Welcome home! This cozy 2 bed 2.5 bath home is perfect for first time buyers or investors looking to add to their rental portfolio! Walking in you're greeted with gorgeous, warm hardwoods throughout. Family room is ideal for entertaining with the open concept flow from kitchen with white cabinetry to the dining area. 2nd level has a roommate floor plan with 2 oversized bedrooms and 2 full baths! New roof and new water heater as well!! This will not last long!
